=Description=

"In this Screencast I tried to explain what "[[Distributed Social Networking]]" is all about. I talk shortly about the building blocks of social networking in general, then point out where the problem is and show you with Noserub how a Distributed Social Network can work.

This screencast doesn't go to much into technical details and has the objective to make people understand quickly, what it's all about."


